LINE.Text: If you want to make the world a better place, it's a good idea
to find out where you're starting from. When we did just that,
the results came as something of a surprise. By most measures, living
standards are improving across the world, and though hundreds of
millions of people still live in desperate conditions, things are moving
in the right direction. Less encouragingly, the environment is clearly
in trouble and armed conflict remains a major problem
